# TRUSTED_PROXY_HOSTS — comma-separated IPs/CIDRs of trusted upstream proxies
# (or "*" when you KNOW the app is behind a proxy network like Coolify's internal Docker network).
# Default empty = do not trust X-Forwarded-For; use the TCP peer IP.
# vibe-gatekeeper prod is currently direct-exposed (http://IP:8080, no proxy), so leave empty.
# TRUSTED_PROXY_HOSTS=
